      "beat_id": "B02",
      "t_start": 9.0,
      "estimated_duration_s": 9.0,
      "narration_text": "Drop a marble in a box \u2014 it rolls to the bottom and stops. Energy: zero. That's classical mechanics and it makes complete sense.",
