    {
      "beat_id": "B03",
      "t_start": 18.0,
      "estimated_duration_s": 10.0,
      "narration_text": "Now the quantum version. There's a box. A particle inside. Classical prediction: the lowest energy should be zero \u2014 just sit still. It doesn't. Why?",
