      "beat_id": "B10",
      "t_start": 90.0,
      "estimated_duration_s": 12.0,
      "narration_text": "Illustrative example: a 1-nanometer box. The ground state energy works out to about 0.38 electron-volts \u2014 visible light carries around 2 eV. That gap is real and measurable.",
